# Vision Environment Requirement

`record_scan.py` depends on `pyorbbecsdk` and `cv2`, which are only installed in the **vision** conda env.

Always run with:

```bash
/home/lq/miniconda3/envs/vision/bin/python docker_all/components/monty_comp/app/monty_ext/scripts/record_scan.py [args...]
```

Never use `tbp.monty` env or bare `python` — they lack the camera SDK.
